metadata.title: Design Toscano AL958699 Japanese Pagoda Illuminated Lantern Statue: Set of Two,greystone
features: Solar Lights - Concealed, cordless solar lights gently shine to highlight the graceful Asian shape of these rectangular pagodas with hoshu kasa umbrella roofs, curved kidan legs and hibukuro lattice fronts
Serene Patio - Usher in serenity and peace to your zen, Japanese garden or other sacred space with these illuminated sculptures! They are sure to bring attention to your backyard deck day or night
High Quality Sculpture - Hand-cast using real crushed stone bonded with durable designer resin, our pagoda statues are then topped with a UV resistant faux stone finish
Design Toscano Asian Statue - Exclusive to the Design Toscano brand, these garden statues are a beautiful representation of Asian culture for home or yard display and they also makes unique gifts
Our statues each measure 11"Wx6"Dx16.5"H and weigh 4 lbs. perfect for a tranquil spot on a serene backyard patio. Solar panel has on/off button. Takes one AA battery each.
description: Usher in serenity and peace to your Zen, Japanese garden or other sacred space! A concealed, cordless solar light gently shines to highlight the graceful Asain shape of this rectangular, Design Toscano exclusive. We've carefully cast details from the hoshu kasa umbrella roof, the curved kidan legs and the hibukuro lattice front in quality designer resin with a textured, faux stone finish that makes our sculpture quintessentially Oriental! 11"Wx6"Dx16½"H. 4 lbs.
